  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you would knock a creature back more than 5 feet with a melee weapon attack or Bukijutsu, you can immediately use Brave Dash at no cost to dash toward the creature and make one melee weapon attack, dealing your weapon's damage + 1 flurry die on a hit.</p><p> The creature must then make a Dexterity saving throw, being knocked back 30 feet in any direction on a failed save.</p><p> You can use this style no more than once per turn.</p><p></p>",
